<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Our Services</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="">
  <style>
    body{
      
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container{
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 1400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
  
    }
 
  .service{
display: flex;
margin: 60px;
background-color: rgb(211, 206, 206);
padding: 60px;
border-radius: 10px;
  }

  .service-2, .service-4{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row-reverse;
    margin: 60px;
  }
  .service-6{
    margin-top: 50px;
  }
  .service-6 h3 {
    text-align:center;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 900;
  }
  .service-6 p{
    font-weight: 900;
    width: 50%;
    text-align: center;
    margin:30px  auto;
  }


  .img{
    width: 50%;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 0 30px;
  }
  .img img{
    width: 50%;
  }
  .lease,.pay,.maintain,.screenig,.listings{
    width: 40%;
  }
  #list{
    margin-left: -20%;
  }
  .intro{
  margin: 0 auto;
  text-align: center;
  }
.intro{ animation: glow 5s ease-in-out infinite;
            
             text-align: center;
             }
             @keyframes glow { 0%
                 { text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff, 0 0 10px #fff, 0 0 15px #fff, 0 0 20px #f00, 0 0 35px #f00, 0 0 40px #f00, 0 0 50px #f00, 0 0 75px #f00; } 
             50% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff, 0 0 10px #fff, 0 360px 15px #fff, 0 0 20px #0f0, 0 0 35px #0f0, 0 0 40px #0f0, 0 0 50px #0f0, 0 0 75px #0f0; } 
             100% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px #fff, 0 0 10px #fff, 0 0 15px #fff, 0 0 20px #f00, 0 0 35px #f00, 0 0 40px #f00, 0 0 50px #f00, 0 0 75px #f00; } }
        

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("_header123.ejs") %>
  <div class="container">
  <div class="intro">
   <h1>Our Services</h1>
      <p>We offer a wide range of services to help you manage your real estate and rental properties, including:</p>
  </div>
     
    <div class="service">
      
      <div class="img">
        <img src="/images/lease.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
        <img src="/images/lease1.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
      </div>
      <div class="lease">
        <h3>Lease Management</h3>
        <p>We provide a comprehensive lease management system that allows you to easily manage your leases and keep track of your tenants' information.</p>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    <div class="service-2">
      <div class="img">
        <img src="/images/maintenance1.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
      <img src="/images/main3.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
      </div>

      <div class="maintain">
        <h3>Maintenance Requests</h3>
        <p>We offer a maintenance request system that allows your tenants to easily submit maintenance requests and track their progress.</p>
      </div>
      
     
    </div>
    <div class="service">
      <div class="img">
        <img src="/images/payment.png" alt="Service 1">
      <img src="/images/payment2.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
      </div>
      <div class="pay">
        <h3>Payment Processing</h3>
        <p>We provide a secure payment processing system that allows your tenants to easily pay their rent and other fees online.</p>
      </div>
     
    </div>
    <div class="service-4">
      <div class="img">
        <img src="/images/screenig.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
      <img src="/images/screening1.jpeg" alt="Service 1">
      </div>
      <div class="screenig">
        <h3>Tenant Screening</h3>
        <p>We offer a tenant screening service that allows you to thoroughly vet your tenants and ensure that they are reliable and trustworthy.</p>
      </div>
      
    </div>
    <div class="service">
      <div class="img">
        <img src="/images/listings.png" alt="Service 1">
      </div>
      <div class="listings" id="list">
        <h3>Property Listings</h3>
        <p>We provide a property listing service that allows you to easily list your properties and attract potential tenants.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="service-6">
      
            <h3>And Much More!</h3>
      <p>We offer a wide range of additional services to help you manage your real estate and rental properties. Contact us today to learn more about how we can help you streamline your investments and improve their income.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>